<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Platform</title>
    <style>
        /* You can add CSS styles here for formatting */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #000080;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .line {
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc; /* Define line style */
            margin: 10px 0; /* Adjust margin for positioning */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Platform, {{ firstName }}!</h1>
        </div>
        <hr class="line">
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are excited to have you join us. Your account has been successfully created.</p>
            <p>Your password has been automatically generated:</p>
            <p><strong>{{ password }}</strong></p>
            <p>You can now log in using your email address and the password above.</p>
            <p>Thank you and enjoy your experience on our platform!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was automatically generated. Please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
